1acb9e77328053e58148fb19c131bebeb9ce7fd9.query:

            WHERE state_root IN (
                SELECT state_root FROM beacon_states
                WHERE slot >= $1
            )

            ON CONFLICT (key) DO UPDATE SET
                value = excluded.value

96699a3966db2fe2de98dc9cd0db41276406bafb.query:

                blocks
            (
                base_fee_per_gas,
                gas_used,
                hash,
                mined_at,
                number
            )

                $1,
                $2,
                $3,
                $4,
                $5
            )

                block_root,
                state_root,
                parent_root,

f51ac89ed5030a134d406f4f1595abd2af118630.query:
SELECT
                beacon_states.state_root,
                beacon_states.slot,
                beacon_blocks.block_root AS "block_root?"
            FROM beacon_states
            LEFT JOIN beacon_blocks ON beacon_blocks.state_root = beacon_states.state_root
            ORDER BY slot DESC
            LIMIT 1
